         <abstract id="aspace_e4768e07d3b305605f99dfcd9abdc7ab">The collection consists of correspondence, organizational records, personal papers, daily calendars, photographs, sermons, poetry, research materials, and other writings that document the activities and research of Samuel Gruenberg.</abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_c0108ac59693d0c1dff39d8db4557f8a">
